  <section class="hero" id="hero">
    <h1>We’re a design, technology and research studio who help people be their best</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="services" id="services">
    <aside>
      <div>
        <img src="/assets/jaye.jpg" alt="Jaye Hackett"/>
        <img src="/assets/chloe.jpg" alt="Chloe Coleman"/>
      </div>

      <p>We founded Interrobang because we wanted to get back to basics: delivering real user-led change in the public sector.</p>
      <p>Our participatory approach sees the world through three lenses.</p>
      <dl>
        <dd>40+</dd>
        <dt>public and third sector clients</dt>
      </dl>
    </aside>

    <ul class="tile-list">
      <li class="tile-list__tile">
        <h2>Research</h2>
        <p>For us, everything starts with building a deep, empathetic understanding of users and their needs.</p>
        <p>This involves:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Turning prior work into hypotheses, so we don’t re-invent the wheel</li>
          <li>One-to-one interviews</li>
          <li>Interactive workshops</li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li class="tile-list__tile">
        <h2>Design</h2>
        <p>We do participatory, user-led design that marries the lived experience of your users with our expertise.</p>
        <p>In practice, this means lots of:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>design sprints</li>
          <li>co-design workshops</li>
          <li>prototyping things and getting early feedback</li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li class="tile-list__tile">
        <h2>Technology</h2>
        <p>We are technology-agnostic. We don't chase trends. Instead, we’ll consider things like:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>sustainable upfront and ongoing costs</li>
          <li>the ease of keeping things up and running after the project</li>
          <li>a good fit to your context and the skills of your staff</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="values" id="values">
    <img src="/assets/values.jpg" alt="#"/>

    <div>
      <h2>Our values</h2>
      <p>Our people come from all places and backgrounds. Civil service, creative agencies. Our participatory approach means that we don’t try to be the experts: we find and empower the experts that already exist in the community, and help them raise their voices.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

